data.description: Handicap assessible! This three bedroom, two bathroom 2002 manufactured home is nestled on a quiet private drive in the Central Orchards close to schools and shopping. Features spacious living room, private fully fenced back yard, large double car garage. New tankless hot water heater, newer furnace. Large master bedroom with walk in closet. Beautiful tile in the kitchen and a nice center island that has an open concept family room off the kitchen.
